#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as the screen saver starts. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Zatvorite novčanik ubrzo nakon što se pokrene čuvar zaslona. Kada je "
"novčanik zatvoren, potrebna je šifra za ponovni pristup njemu."

#. Tag: guilabel
