#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click with the &LMB; on the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> symbol beside a wallet "
"name to expand the tree. You will see the name of each application that has "
"asked for access to the wallet, and the policy you set for it. You cannot "
"edit policies here, or add them, but it is possible to delete an entry by "
"&RMB; clicking on it and choosing <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> from the "
"context menu that appears, or by simply selecting it and pressing the "
"<keysym>Del</keysym> key."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite sa &LMB; na <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> simbol pored novčanika da "
"proširite drvo. Vidjet ćete ime svake aplikacije koja je zatražila pristup "
"novčaniku, i politike koje ste Vi podesili za njih. Ne možete uređivati "
"politike ovdje, ili ih dodavati, ali je moguće brisanje unosa pomoću &RMB;-a "
"klikom na njega i odabirom<guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem> sa kontekstnog "
"izbornika koji se pojavi, ili jednostavno odabiranjem njega i pritiskom na  "
"<keysym>Del</keysym> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An application that has been allowed access to a wallet is granted access to "
"all passwords stored inside."
msgstr ""
"Aplikaciji kojoj je omogućen pristup novčaniku je garantiran pristup svim "
"šifrana koje su pohranjene unutra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you erroneously configured an application not to use the &kde; "
#| "&kwalletmanager; delete the policy for this application here."
msgid ""
"If you erroneously configured an application not to use the &kwallet5; "
"delete the policy for this application here."
msgstr ""
"Ako pogrešno konfigurišete aplikaciju da ne koristi &kde;-ov "
"&kwalletmanager; obrišite politiku za ovu aplikaciju ovdje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next start of this application you can define a new policy for access "
"to the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Na narednom pokretanju ove aplikacije možete definirati novu politiku za "
"pristup novčaniku."

