msgstr "Napredne značajke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Wallets can be dragged from the &kwalletmanager; window. This allows you "
#| "to drag the wallet to a file browser window, where you can choose to "
#| "copy, move, or link the wallet, as desired."
msgid ""
"Wallets can be dragged from the &kwalletmanager5; window. This allows you to "
"drag the wallet to a file browser window, where you can choose to copy, "
"move, or link the wallet, as desired."
msgstr ""
"Novčanici mogu biti dovučeni iz &kwalletmanager; prozora. Ovo Vam omogućava "
"da dovlačite novčanite u prozor pretraživača datoteka, gdje možete izabrati "
"da kopirate, pomjerate, ili linkujete novčanik, kako poželite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might use this to save a wallet to portable media, such as a USB "
"keychain, so that you can take your passwords with you to work or on a "
"vacation, and still have easy access to important sites."
msgstr ""
"Ovo možete koristiti da spasite novčanik na prenosni medij, kao što je USB, "
"tako da možete nositi Vaše šifre uz sebe na posao ili odmor, a i dalje imate "
"lahak pristup bitnim stranicama."

